** Heading +Sym
** CalculiX implicit transient dynamic template
** Rendered by AI-FEA Solver Agent from SimPlan parameters.
**
** Variables (Jinja2):
**   mesh_include   — path to .inp mesh file
**   material_name  — e.g. "Steel"
**   youngs_modulus  — Pa
**   poissons_ratio
**   density_kg_m3   — kg/m3
**   damping_alpha   — Rayleigh Mass Proportional Damping
**   damping_beta    — Rayleigh Stiffness Proportional Damping
**   load_magnitude  — N
**   load_node_set   — name of the node set receiving the load
**   fixed_node_set  — name of the fixed-BC node set
**
*INCLUDE, INPUT={{ mesh_include }}
**
** MATERIAL
*MATERIAL, NAME={{ material_name }}
*DENSITY
{{ density_kg_m3 | default(7850) }}
*ELASTIC
{{ youngs_modulus }}, {{ poissons_ratio }}
{% if yield_strength_pa %}
*PLASTIC
{{ yield_strength_pa }}, 0.0
{% if tangent_modulus_pa %}
{{ yield_strength_pa + tangent_modulus_pa * 1.0 }}, 1.0
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
{% if damping_alpha is not none and damping_beta is not none %}
*DAMPING, ALPHA={{ damping_alpha }}, BETA={{ damping_beta }}
{% endif %}
**
** SOLID SECTION (assumes single part)
*SOLID SECTION, ELSET=Eall, MATERIAL={{ material_name }}
**
** BOUNDARY CONDITIONS
*BOUNDARY
{{ fixed_node_set }}, 1, 3, 0.0
**
** STEP
*STEP{% if nonlinear %}, NLGEOM=ON{% endif %}
*DYNAMIC
** initial_time_step, total_time, min_step, max_step
0.01, 1.0, 1e-5, 0.1
**
** LOADS
*CLOAD
{{ load_node_set }}, 2, {{ load_magnitude }}
**
** OUTPUT
*NODE FILE
U, V, A
*EL FILE
S, E
**
*END STEP
